text: KWOF may refer to: * KWOF (FM), a radio station (106.3 FM) licensed to serve Waukomis, Oklahoma, United States * KKSE-FM, a radio station (92.5 FM) licensed to serve Broomfield, Colorado, United States, which held the call sign KWOF from 2009 to 2018 * KXGM (FM), a radio stataion (89.1 FM) licensed to serve Hiawatha, Iowa, United States, which held the call sign KWOF-FM from 2002 to 2008 * KXGM (AM), a defunct radio station (850 AM) licensed to serve Waterloo, Iowa, which held the call sign KWOF from 1985 to 2008
title: KWOF
